 🎬 Netflix Clone

A || Netflix UI Clone ||  built with HTML | CSS | JavaScript that mimics the look and feel of the official Netflix website. This project demonstrates responsive design, modern UI practices, and can be extended with API integration for real data.


---

 📋 Features

- 🎞️ Beautiful and modern homepage with hero banner
- 📺 Movie rows and categories layout similar to Netflix
- 📱 Fully responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- 🔍 Hover effects and smooth transitions
- 🖼️ Dynamic movie thumbnails and banners
- 🧑 Profile and navbar UI (mock version)

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Structure and layout  
- CSS3 – Styling, animations, and responsiveness  
- JavaScript (ES6) – Interactivity (sliders, buttons, etc.)  
- Vercel – Deployment (for live demo)

